The paper deals with range searching and reporting, which are fundamental problems in computational geometry (cs.CG). It also involves the use of data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms for semi-algebraic sets (cs.DM). The applications mentioned in the paper involve optimization and numerical analysis (cs.SC, cs.NA).
